snippet.title: Evercade Gremlin Collection 1 Gameplay Showcase
snippet.description:
A look into the six games coming with Gremlin Collection 1 to Evercade in March 2022. Pre-orders open on December 15th! Secure your copy today.!

Games List:
🖤 Zool
📈 Premier Manager 97
⚽ Actua Soccer
🏗️ Utopia: The Creation of a Nation
🏁 Hardcore 4X4
⚪ Brain Bender

All footage was captured from Evercade hardware.

More info: https://evercade.co.uk/cartridges/gremlin-collection-1
Pre-Order: https://evercade.co.uk/retailers
